snippet.title: Super Fishing
snippet.description: Super Fishing Fishing game. Try to catch as many fish as you can. Complete the challenges to earn more cash.

snippet.title: Raid Mission
snippet.description: Raid Mission Guide the elite squad through dangerous missions in which you need to defeat all the scum.

snippet.title: Decision 2: New City
snippet.description: Decision 2: New City Shooting game. Get rid of the zombies and complete all of the missions to stay alive.

snippet.title: Dibbles 4: Xmas Crisis
snippet.description: Dibbles 4: Xmas Crisis Puzzle adventure. Get Santa to reach the exit of each level using the special skills of the dibbles.

snippet.title: Beach Tennis
snippet.description: Beach Tennis Missy and Candi return in 3D. Beach Tennis has never been so fun.

snippet.title: Twister Island
snippet.description: Twister Island Taz has landed on a lost tropical Island. Help him to escape by destroying all the Stone Statues.

snippet.title: Elite Forces: Mission Afghanistan
snippet.description: Elite Forces: Mission Afghanistan You are stationed in Afghanistan, clear the area and wipe out all enemy forces.

snippet.title: Hobo Prison Brawl
snippet.description: Hobo Prison Brawl Use special combos to spit, shit and pee on the prisoners and guards and try to escape the prison.

snippet.title: Palisade Guardian 3
snippet.description: Palisade Guardian 3 First person shooting game. Destroy all the incoming alien units and earn cash to upgrade your skills.

snippet.title: Chisel 2
snippet.description: Chisel 2 Arcade game. Try to drill all planets apart and collect diamonds and gems to proceed to the next level.
